le=\"kacalisian 2019 5\"\n        src=\"/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg 180w,\n/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg 360w,\n/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg 720w,\n/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/72109/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg 1080w,\n/static/842d59dc1405e14187bd5b1c76569beb/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-5.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>藝術家 Live 創作！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 6\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 6\"\n        src=\"/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg 180w,\n/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg 360w,\n/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg 720w,\n/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/72109/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg 1080w,\n/static/5652c675f5b6cc527c6ddae0d74ca50b/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-6.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>泰武古謠傳唱</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 7\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 7\"\n        src=\"/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg 180w,\n/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg 360w,\n/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg 720w,\n/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/72109/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg 1080w,\n/static/1d98a8b4d3c4ce132b3a59868b0e0552/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-7.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>戴曉君</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 8\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 8\"\n        src=\"/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg 180w,\n/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg 360w,\n/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg 720w,\n/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/72109/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg 1080w,\n/static/72557f21a894791a1715a2b0e72653f9/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-8.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>動力火車</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 10\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 10\"\n        src=\"/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg 180w,\n/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg 360w,\n/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg 720w,\n/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/72109/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg 1080w,\n/static/fad618c2e03f640645e613856dc7281a/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-10.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>動力火車</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 9\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 9\"\n        src=\"/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg 180w,\n/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg 360w,\n/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg 720w,\n/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/72109/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg 1080w,\n/static/aa5cb439554b9cda889bf2d0d64a9ec8/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-9.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>動力火車